{"tid":152382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂天原來一直有幫支那起小學,愛支賊點解唔封小學呀?","createTime":"2017-03-11T16:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T10:48:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74111aad3194da7e40c96f60e7cf87696a461f77","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【立此存照】除了小熊&amp;#39292;，&amp;#20048;天&amp;#36824;有希望小&amp;#23398;/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinadigitaltimes.net%2Fchinese%2F2017%2F03%2F%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%B0%8F%E7%86%8A%26%2339292%3B%EF%BC%8C%26%2320048%3B%E5%A4%A9%26%2336824%3B%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%B0%8F%26%2323398%3B%2F&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C0%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=65c08943\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/03/【立此存照】除了小熊&amp;#39292;，&amp;#20048;天&amp;#36824;有希望小&amp;#23398;/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國網｜&ldquo;一社一校&rdquo;樂天集團助力教育事業（2016年11月）<br />\n<br />\n樂天集團自2008年起，在甘肅、陝西、安徽、江西、四川、江蘇、遼寧等多地支援建設了希望小學，解決了周邊學生亟待就讀的問題，也得到了當地青少年發展基金會、政府部門、教育局、團委等機構的支持。樂天希望小學現惠及各地學生七百餘名，省市縣級獲獎優秀學生及教師十餘名，預計三年後學生總數將達千餘名。<br />\n<br />\n新華網｜四川LOTTE樂天希望小學竣工在歡笑中追逐未來（2015年11月）<br />\n<br />\n此番樂天希望小學竣工儀式得到了樂天集團中國總部、樂天百貨（成都）有限公司、樂天地產（成都）有限公司、樂天瑪特（成都）商業有限公司以及四川省青基會、樂山市委、團市委、犍為縣政府、犍為縣教體局等相關政府領導的積極參與。<br />\n<br />\n部分樂天希望小學：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/KrAzcl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FKrAzcl.jpg&h=188a072e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨用核彈炸鳩D支那樂天小學, 再起過, 又有GDP, 豆腐渣, 貪官偷笑</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2f3914d592cbf915e84c6a21318a0f59ec34342b","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T17:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb830e6472b6139fdce080ee489683d4ac33ecda","tid":152382,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T18:09:12.000Z","msg":"中國全球經濟體第二仲要啲集團呀名人有錢佬捐錢，幾時聽過日本仔要其他國家捐錢起學校"},{"pid":"3b9786575a885b763be356be89bc36fe447ce406","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2868d93af231532845f58a6fea4b36b2ef300c12","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54981e1f1470e8abcb51b282a3c93622770c56d5","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5742b845891c6cc606a72b0239fab49ecd1460b4","tid":152382,"uid":82528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"大陸狗又選擇性失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a10073a1fb60325c3806f82860aa32dbe16e0f","tid":152382,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T04:40:30.000Z","msg":"快啲拆晒啲學校 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766acb97cc7c822b1d541c27eab593177f554594","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b8ca7d2b21534523df4ed0badf6c4c5c087567","tid":152382,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f726f8e42f7b2b7c2bf2e0931d6b9fc47d7ce8a","tid":152382,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl